articles.title: US figure skaters awarded Olympic gold after Russian skater disqualified - CNN
articles.description: The US will receive a gold medal for its 2022 Beijing Winter Olympic team ice skating performance, but Canada was snubbed from bronze after Russian figure skater Kamila Valieva was handed a four-year ban over a long-running doping controversy.
